apps.description:
"On FFSAY, you can communicate in an extremely safe environment, securely encrypted message transmission in multiple formats such as text, voice, pictures, etc. to ensure that the security of your messages is foolproof, and you can chat happily, chat with peace of mind. More It has powerful and diverse group management functions, supports banning screenshots in the group, restricts sending business cards and other advanced group setting functions, protects the privacy of group chats and ensures the security of your chats

  Main function introduction:
-Purely secure message communication, text, voice, pictures, GIF, video, all types of messages in multiple formats are safely encrypted and transmitted to ensure that your privacy is never leaked;
-Powerful group management function, the group owner and administrator can set special speech fonts and colors for themselves to be the most beautiful person in the group. You can also set up functions such as banning screenshots in the group, restricting sending business cards, restricting speech, etc. to ensure order within the group and protect the privacy of group members;
-Group sensitive word filtering, automatically detects and intercepts inappropriate remarks and confidential information, creates a harmonious group atmosphere, and ensures that confidential information is not leaked;
-Group inactive user management, you can view and restrict inactive users, streamline group members, and improve group activity;
-Plaza, you can check the latest news, share the beautiful scenery you have seen, the delicious food you have eaten, and the happy moments with your family;
-Multiple account switching, you can add different accounts after logging in, and switch multiple accounts safely with one click;"

