apps.description:
Stay connected to your customers and staff on the go. 
The Sinch mobile application makes business messaging easier, faster, and more effective.
• Get real-time push notifications so you never miss any important communication;
• Reply to SMS from a shared team inbox;
• Quickly send individual or mass SMS messages to your contacts;
• Assign conversations to your teammates;
• View customer details and start texting in seconds;
• Switch between subaccounts to manage conversations across multiple teams;
• Use business phone numbers for communication with your contacts and keep your work and personal life separate;
• Use templates for faster communication.
Simple. Powerful. Business messaging, wherever you are.

